PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ?dog ?age WHERE {
  ?dog wdt:P31 wd:Q144 .
  ?dog wdt:P569 ?birthDate .
  ?dog wdt:P570 ?deathDate .
  BIND( year( ?deathDate ) - year( ?birthDate ) AS ?age )
}
ORDER BY DESC ( ?age )
LIMIT 1
OFFSET 1

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?discipline ?germanName WHERE {
  ?discipline wdt:P31 wd:Q11862829 .
  ?discipline rdfs:label ?germanName .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?germanName ) = "de" ) FILTER ( CONTAINS( LCASE( ?germanName ) , "linguistik" ) )
}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ?game ?releaseDate WHERE {
  ?game wdt:P178 wd:Q677273 ; wdt:P577 ?releaseDate .
}
ORDER BY ?releaseDate
LIMIT 1
OFFSET 1

PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
ASK WHERE {
  wd:Q169452 p:P54 [ ps:P54 wd:Q121783 ; pq:P580 ?start1 ; pq:P582 ?end1 ] .
  wd:Q25369 p:P54 [ ps:P54 wd:Q121783 ; pq:P580 ?start2 ; pq:P582 ?end2 ] .
  FILTER ( ?start1 <= "2000-01-01T00:00:00Z" ^^ xsd:dateTime && ?end1 >= "2000-01-01T00:00:00Z" ^^ xsd:dateTime ) FILTER ( ?start2 <= "2000-01-01T00:00:00Z" ^^ xsd:dateTime && ?end2 >= "2000-01-01T00:00:00Z" ^^ xsd:dateTime )
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
SELECT ( COUNT( DISTINCT ?resort ) AS ?count ) WHERE {
  ?resort wdt:P31 wd:Q130003 ; p:P17 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P17 wd:Q142 .
}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ?member ?dateOfBirth WHERE {
  wd:Q51885404 wdt:P527 ?member .
  ?member wdt:P569 ?dateOfBirth .
}

PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?president ?presidentLabel ?startDate WHERE {
  ?president wdt:P39 wd:Q56024 ; p:P39 ?positionStatement .
  ?positionStatement pq:P580 ?startDate .
  OPTIONAL {
    ?positionStatement pq:P582 ?endDate
  }
  FILTER ( IF( BOUND( ?endDate ) , ?endDate > NOW () , true ) ) ?president rdfs:label ?presidentLabel .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?presidentLabel ) = "en" )
}
ORDER BY DESC ( ?startDate )
LIMIT 1

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ?article ?date WHERE {
  ?article wdt:P921 wd:Q6557482 .
  ?article wdt:P577 ?date
}
ORDER BY ASC ( ?date )
LIMIT 1

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
ASK WHERE {
  wd:Q183 p:P1082 ?statement2010 .
  ?statement2010 ps:P1082 ?population2010 ; pq:P585 ?time2010 .
  FILTER ( YEAR( ?time2010 ) = 2010 ) .
  wd:Q183 p:P1082 ?statementCurrent .
  ?statementCurrent ps:P1082 ?currentPopulation .
  BIND( ( ( ?currentPopulation - ?population2010 ) / ?population2010 * 100 ) AS ?growthRate ) FILTER ( ?growthRate >= 1 )
}

}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT DISTINCT ?album ?albumLabel WHERE {
  ?album wdt:P31 wd:Q482994 .
  ?album wdt:P175 wd:Q238819 .
  ?album wdt:P577 ?releaseDate .

    ?album rdfs:label ?albumLabel .
    FILTER ( LANG( ?albumLabel ) = "en" )
  }

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?show ?showLabel WHERE {
  ?show wdt:P31 wd:Q5398426 .
  ?show wdt:P580 ?startDate .
  FILTER ( ?startDate >= '1975-10-07' ^^ xsd:date && ?startDate <= '1975-10-13' ^^ xsd:date ) .
  FILTER ( ?show != wd:Q13979 ) .
  OPTIONAL {
    ?show rdfs:label ?showLabel .
    FILTER ( LANG( ?showLabel ) = 'en' )
  }
}
LIMIT 100

PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
